1991;;Sam and Me;;Canadian;;Deepa Mehta;;Ranjit Chowdhry, Peter Boretski, Om Puri;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sam_and_Me;;23-year-old Nikhil, an Indian immigrant, is convinced by his uncle to work as a companion and care-giver to Sam, an elderly Jewish man, fed up with his life. As an unlikely friendship ensues, both men get new insight into life.[3]